hopobject.body: Where do you live? can you get high off bupropion sr 150 mg The wealth of medical symptom information now readily available online has inevitably contributed to the rise of the 'cyberchondriac' ; those who spend hours attributing every ache and pain to a dramatic twist of health misfortune. Whilst the internet has done wonders to raise awareness of illness and warning signs, be sure to visit a doctor before self-diagnosing your caffeine withdrawal headache as a brain tumour.
